Requirements
------------

* Python (2.7, 3.2, 3.3, 3.4, 3.5)
* Django (1.8, 1.9, 1.10)


Installation
------------

Install oauth2_package using `pip`...

```
  pip install django-oauth2-package
```

Add to the bottom of your settings.py

```
from oauth2_package.settings import *
```

Add to urls.py

```
urlpatterns = [
    url(r'^admin/', admin.site.urls),
    url(r'^auth/', include('oauth2_package.urls')),
    ...
]

```

Add logo to login dialog

```
  LOGIN_FORM_LOGO = ''
```
